h2(#description). Description


This tag is used to display a list of languages for a page. Take a look at the header. There you
will find a link titled 'en'. This is the link to the english (=en) version of this page.


h2(#examples). Examples


This page is available in several other languages (however, with nearly no content :-)) for
demonstration purposes.


